  accentWord="Fire Protection"
  subhead="You post photos of a completed fire stopping installation in a riser shaft. A building manager messages about fire door compliance for their block. Your AI captures the brief while you mastic seals."
  scenario="It is 9:30pm on a Wednesday. A Responsible Person for a converted warehouse complex in East Oxford — four floors, twenty-two flats, shared corridors, and a commercial unit on the ground floor — has received a fire risk assessment with urgent recommendations. The assessor has identified: missing fire stopping at service penetrations on every floor, a communal fire alarm that does not meet L2 standard, three fire doors that fail the gap test, and a smoke ventilation system that has not been serviced in three years. She finds your Facebook page through a recommendation in a building management Facebook group and messages: 'Hi — we have just received a fire risk assessment with urgent findings across a converted warehouse complex. Multiple issues: fire stopping missing, alarm not to L2, fire doors failing, and smoke vent not maintained. 22 flats, 4 floors, commercial ground floor. Can you handle all of this? We need to respond to the assessment within 8 weeks.' Without AI Messenger, you see the message Thursday morning between tasks. She has also messaged two other firms; one replied Wednesday night with a structured list of the four disciplines they cover. With AI Messenger, the reply arrives at 9:31pm — addressing each deficiency category — and she confirms the building address. Thursday morning you open the lead: converted warehouse, OX4, 22 flats over 4 floors, commercial ground floor, fire stopping missing, L2 alarm upgrade needed, 3 failing fire doors, smoke vent service required, 8-week assessment response deadline, address confirmed. You call at 9am and book a Friday morning survey."
  benefits={benefits}
  faqs={faqs}
  channelPageUrl="/construction-trades/ai-facebook-messenger/"
  tradePageUrl="/fire-protection/ai-receptionist/"
  ctaHeadline="Turn FIRAS Certificate Posts into Multi-Block Remediation Contracts"
  ctaSubhead={`A riser before-and-after earns a hundred and sixty likes. AI Messenger converts every building manager enquiry into a survey with deficiency details and compliance deadlines. Add-on at £${pricing.addOn.price}/month.`}
/>
